<para id="element-81">We should emphasize that angular momentum about center of mass is not the same as about an axis of rotation. However, the angular momentum about center of mass is same as angular momentum about axis of rotation passing through center of mass in cases where point (origin) and center of mass are in the plane of motion. In such case, 
