</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-85">
In words, the net external torque on the system of particles is equal to the time rate of change of angular momentum.
</para>
<para id="element-86">
<term>2: </term> Newton’s second law of motion for rotation of a rigid body  is given as :
</para>
<para id="element-87">
